Viola Jones
############

Python implementation of the face detection algorithm by Paul Viola and Michael J. Jones.

Install
=======

Run:

    pip install -e <path to viola-jones>

How to use
==========

See either ``example.py`` or Jupyter notebook ``Viola-Jones Example.ipynb``.


